university of california santa cruz his doctoral research focused on the interaction between long term shifts in global climate and tropical ocean atmosphere dynamics stanford departments law publications cover measuring the clean development mechanism's performance and potential michael wara ucla law review vol 55 6 2008 pdf+ cover a realistic policy on international carbon offsets michael wara david g victor program on energy and sustainable development working paper 74 2008 pdf+ measuring the clean development mechanism's performance and potential wp 56 michael wara program on energy and sustainable development working paper 56 2006 pdf+ fact sheet measuring the clean development mechanism's performance and potential michael wara gordon conference on science and technology policy pdf+ search people everything recent commentary dr michael wara testified before the house agriculture subcommittee on conservation credit energy and research december 5 2009 in the news michael wara speaks at a hearing of the senate energy and natural resources committee september 17 2009 in the news cash for clunkers not cost effective for carbon dioxide emissions reduction in the news new york times on august 14 2009 michael wara on lessons to be learned from the european cap and trade system in the news green inc new york times on may 8 2009 wara and victor quoted in discover magazine on cdm in the news discover magazine on december 1 2008 more commentary about michael wara news around the web going green er planning the next era of environmental regulation in india according to michael wara a law professor and research fellow at stanford university's freeman spogli institute for international studies october 21 2010 in knowledge wharton carbon markets the smoking greenhouse gun they found the smoking gun says michael wara a professor at stanford law school since the executive board received that submission in july september 2 2010 in the economist bp may lose us oil leases contracts